## File and Directory Naming

### Game Directory Structure
- Game directories should use kebab-case: `snake`, `tic-tac-toe`, `memory-match`
- Avoid spaces or special characters in directory names
- Use descriptive, English names

### Component Files
- React components use PascalCase: `GameCard.jsx`, `Header.jsx`
- Utility files use camelCase: `gameLoader.js`, `userSettings.js`
- Style files match component names: `Header.css`, `GameCard.css`

### Image Files
- Use descriptive names: `cover.png`, `thumbnail.jpg`
- Avoid generic names like `image1.png`
- Use consistent naming across games

## Text Content Standards

### Welcome Messages
```jsx
// Home page welcome text
<h1>Welcome to GameTime Bar</h1>
<p>Discover and play a variety of fun web games</p>
```

### Navigation Labels
